at our southern border every day Customs

00:00:12.509 --> 00:00:17.010
and Border Patrol agents encounter
thousands of illegal immigrants trying

00:00:17.010 --> 00:00:22.230
to enter our country we are out of space
to hold them and we have no way to

00:00:22.230 --> 00:00:27.930
promptly return them back home to their
country America proudly welcomes

00:00:27.930 --> 00:00:32.969
millions of lawful immigrants who enrich
our society and contribute to our nation

00:00:32.969 --> 00:00:40.200
but all Americans are hurt by
uncontrolled illegal migration it

00:00:40.200 --> 00:00:46.050
strains public resources and drives down
jobs and wages among those hardest hit

00:00:46.050 --> 00:00:51.360
are African Americans and Hispanic
Americans our southern border is a

00:00:51.360 --> 00:00:57.960
pipeline for vast quantities of illegal
drugs including meth heroin cocaine and

00:00:57.960 --> 00:01:06.000
fentanyl every week 300 of our citizens
are killed by heroin alone 90% of which

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:11.610
floods across from our southern border
more Americans will die from drugs this

00:01:11.610 --> 00:01:18.360
year than were killed in the entire
Vietnam War in the last two years ice

00:01:18.360 --> 00:01:25.920
officers made 266 thousand arrests of
aliens with criminal records including

00:01:25.920 --> 00:01:34.189
those charged or convicted of 100,000
assaults thirty thousand sex crimes and

