00:01:40.619 --> 00:01:45.990
brutally killed by those who illegally
entered our country and thousands more

00:01:45.990 --> 00:01:53.640
lives will be lost if we don't act right
now this is a humanitarian crisis a

00:01:53.640 --> 00:01:59.689
crisis of the heart and a crisis of the
soul last month

00:01:59.689 --> 00:02:04.770
20,000 migrant children were illegally
brought into the United States a

00:02:04.770 --> 00:02:11.360
dramatic increase these children are
used as human pawns by vicious coyotes

00:02:11.360 --> 00:02:14.940
