00:02:28.390 --> 00:02:34.330
illegal immigration on our southern
border this is the cycle of human

00:02:34.330 --> 00:02:41.080
suffering that I am determined to end my
administration has presented Congress

00:02:41.080 --> 00:02:47.890
with a detailed proposal to secure the
border and stop the criminal gangs drug

00:02:47.890 --> 00:02:53.890
