00:03:15.430 --> 00:03:21.310
cutting-edge technology for detecting
drugs weapons illegal contraband and

00:03:21.310 --> 00:03:28.960
many other things we have requested more
agents immigration judges and bed space

00:03:28.960 --> 00:03:34.000
to process the sharp rise and unlawful
migration fueled by our very strong

00:03:34.000 --> 00:03:41.220
economy our plan also contains an urgent
request for humanitarian assistance and

00:03:41.220 --> 00:03:47.710
medical support furthermore we have
asked Congress to close border security

00:03:47.710 --> 00:03:53.460
loopholes so that illegal immigrant
children can be safely and humanely

00:03:53.460 --> 00:04:00.670
