will be a steel barrier rather than a

00:04:11.680 --> 00:04:18.370
concrete wall this barrier is absolutely
critical to border security it's also

00:04:18.370 --> 00:04:22.990
what our professionals at the border
want and need

00:04:22.990 --> 00:04:29.979
